public class GpsLocationProperty extends SierraGxProperty
Property to send a "AT*GPSDATA?" command and to parse a response from a Sierra Wireless GX-series modem containing GPS location information.
Author:
John L. Stanley, Douglas Lau

      protected static Integer parseInteger(String prefix, String str)
      Parse an integer off the end of a string.
      Parameters:
      prefix - Prefix we're looking for.
      str - String to check.
      Returns:
      If it finds the prefix, it returns an Integer containing the numeric value after the prefix. If it doesn't find the prefix or there's no number after the prefix it returns null.
